    "refreshed or removed within 24 hours. Use the budget band and let Amazon",
    "show the live price.",
    "",
    "SPECS ARE TAKEN FROM EACH PRODUCT'S OWN AMAZON TITLE, which is tied to the",
    "specific ASIN. The 'Features & Specs' table on Amazon is NOT reliable for",
    "listings with variants - the UtechSmart Venus table reports Bluetooth /",
    "wireless / 70hr while its title says wired. Always cross-check.",
    "",
    "Fields: id, name, category, budget, asin, verdict (optional), specs,",
    "pick (optional, marks it as a recommendation)."
